
214-Available SITE commands:
214-
214- HELP          - Show this help message
214- RULES         - Show site rules
214- WHO           - Show who's online
214- SWHO          - Staff WHO alias
214- USERS         - List users
214- USER          - Show user details
214- SEEN/LASTON   - Show last login
214- LASTLOGIN     - Last login alias
214- GROUPS        - List groups
214- GROUP/GINFO   - Show group details
214- GRPNFO        - Show group file
214- TRAFFIC       - Show traffic stats
214- CHMOD         - Change file permissions
214- ADDUSER       - Add a new user
214- GADDUSER      - Add a new user to a group
214- DELUSER       - Delete a user (restorable)
214- READD         - Restore a deleted user
214- RENUSER       - Rename a user
214- CHPASS        - Change a user's password
214- ADDIP         - Add IP(s) to a user
214- DELIP         - Delete IP(s) from a user
214- FLAGS         - Change user flags
214- NUKE          - Nuke a release
214- UNNUKE        - Unnuke a release
214- UNDUPE        - Remove release from dupe DB
214- WIPE          - Wipe a path
214- KICK          - Disconnect a user
214- REMERGE       - Refresh slave VFS index
214- XDUPE         - Enable XDUPE mode
214- GRPADD        - Add a group
214- GRPDEL        - Delete a group
214- GADMIN        - Make user group admin
214- CHGRP         - Add user to group
